igure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100539rC46GIfJR9m7MHVn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100538VvFmQdr7JoaLXjxt.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809211005399KGLgunQX40BcOES.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100540Zwz9SgyAb8mCaNKn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100541YH2U0ju8fscRDQkF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Prada 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>“我想试图简化。如今大多数人都不会再穿看上去奇怪的衣服了……也许我们该降低预期。一旦越界，就没人在意你了。但时尚需要人，需要人在意。”<a href=\"https://wwd.com/runway/spring-2019/milan/prada/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">一项以大胆无畏著称的&nbsp;Miuccia Prada 如此说道</a>。<br></p><p>但与此同时，她又为过度简化而忿忿不平。“你们希望时尚被简化成一堆标签吗？就像政治一样？我觉得不该。你简化得越多，就会喜欢用越多标语（slogan），实质性内容就更少了。”</p><p>新系列体现出了&nbsp;Miuccia Prada 内心的这种矛盾。一方面额外装饰被减到了最低，只留下尽量干净利落的廓形，另一方面荧光色、扎染和锁链缠绕状的印花、袜靴、泳装，又是当季潮流。很难说&nbsp;Miuccia Prada 是否为这种自我矛盾找到了答案。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100848xqMFTl69Q75thjuc.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100848TAxMYS2VNwdh89bB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809211008493R87r2oCM0PTKcIH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100849ZFahYIfHE6pkbeXT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018092110084973KCr90RYMcIxzt1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100850N8oBkVzYP94tSrlZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100851zDaUO3TqSldH5YGs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100852mGqaLw9Frz4i8CDK.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100852F36O0ZL4eKSdCguH.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100850fvDc5KxVO4LWYCA2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100853tmAiYcNZVs3hX2Mw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809211008549YRsOTEC5XJeAxZ6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100854oTKWXUw7ZNsfSREv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100854HJgKVTw0POqhC2GR.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100854J1dfQS0aiRAeq5rw.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809211008557hm5av8ZRUSCgT3J.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100855ZBcRh6kKUADSxVFd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100856wkcEl51YpCQDydMN.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100856CnyFX1q5G3bJ9jPB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921100856KG62AEBlnXZs4od0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Moschino 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>新系列看上去就像是设计师直接将草稿放到了 T 台上，那些寥寥几笔的鲜艳印花搭配 80 年代廓形反而乐趣无穷。</p><p>创意总监 Jeremy Scott 带着些自嘲的意味解释说：“ 时尚行业越来越快，快到这次我没法及时完成自己的工作。能给大家看的只有手稿而已。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101725j8k6VxScfvmDUlHs.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101658xdjJXW1erIcM7T8z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101656qhzy7ZcMEloVRHAf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101657o9N57FBbhHgx3PGy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101659K5xkUXpMnWIVFh2s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101700EFfkS8JygtpeWxXQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101701YzwOyk1Jx9rPLfVv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101701ksiV3er0vGjyIcOx.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101702MPbfGvauUiyc1j0x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180921101703a0oSjUfBWnGhX8HQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.499268\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201809211017035PL62f3vj4mk7D1q.jpg\" data-rati